We recommended and the Management agreed that the:
(a)  Municipal Accountant provide allowance for impairment for RPT and SET Receivable;
(b) Municipal Treasurer to (i) intensify efforts to collect long outstanding RPT and SET Receivable and or (ii) initiate civil remedies for the collection thereof.

We commended the Management for the actions taken to implement RA No. 9003.  We recommended that the Solid Waste Management Implementing Group (a) xxx; 

(b) strictly enforce the penalties for the violators of RA No. 9003 and other environmental ordinances; and 

(c) prioritize and implement the approved Ten-Year SWMP in accordance with the requirements of RA No. 9003.
